Radar/ Spider/ Polar Chart

##       [,1]
## red    139
## green   69
## blue    19

As observed in the radarcharts above, coffee profiles (depicted by the radar chart’s shape) across countries appear similar. It is hard to tell for example Ethiopia is rated the highest across most categories.

Median scores of each category in each country were used in the plot.

Supported by the radar chart above where radarcharts of individual countries are plotted overlapping one another, we see that there is very minor difference between countries.

All these despite having different growing conditions such as altitude, harvesting period, types/colour of coffee beans etc.
